  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/523910da136c091c4cbcc6d94d329e78.poster.avif?t=1619088916\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/523910da136c091c4cbcc6d94d329e78.webm?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/523910da136c091c4cbcc6d94d329e78.mp4?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Ancient Abyss is a 2D Zelda-like action game where you will explore mysterious and hidden events in a randomly generated maze. As you progress, you’ll gain more power and collect items to help you reach further into the maze. As you walk through the layers of the maze and reach the bottom of the abyss, you’ll discover mysterious and dark forces, tucked away, so no one would find them...<br><br>Ancient Abyss features the thrilling battle and perma-death mechanics of the Roguelike genre, as well as the exploration and discovery of 2D Zelda games.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/cd39197da1189eea423c84cc73a59956.poster.avif?t=1619088916\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/cd39197da1189eea423c84cc73a59956.webm?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/cd39197da1189eea423c84cc73a59956.mp4?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><strong>• RogueZelda: </strong>An action game that combines RogueLike and 2D Zelda elements, allowing players to experience exploration and discovery in a randomly generated maze. The game combines the depth of a RogueLike game with a thrilling perma-death experience. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/e1d026a1c074cac9d637c618e3c7cf74.poster.avif?t=1619088916\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/e1d026a1c074cac9d637c618e3c7cf74.webm?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/e1d026a1c074cac9d637c618e3c7cf74.mp4?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>• Explore: </strong>The game is full of unreachable and hidden areas, but players have the opportunity to master new skills and acquire new items at any time in the game. These new abilities will help players explore further to discover treasures and secrets hidden within the maze. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/ce73eec61676ceaa9168b2dc6b75e5a5.poster.avif?t=1619088916\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/ce73eec61676ceaa9168b2dc6b75e5a5.webm?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/ce73eec61676ceaa9168b2dc6b75e5a5.mp4?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>• Stimulating Combat: </strong>A wide selection of melee and ranged weaponry allow for multiple styles of play and create a unique combat experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/242aadc9f7bffeba82d911f9bb4fcda2.poster.avif?t=1619088916\" width=512 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/242aadc9f7bffeba82d911f9bb4fcda2.webm?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/242aadc9f7bffeba82d911f9bb4fcda2.mp4?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>• 2D world with dynamic lighting: </strong>Beautiful pixel art, intuitive and smooth animation and excellent dynamic lighting effects create a wonderful visual experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/142cc540828c66cbeff949e246e32086.poster.avif?t=1619088916\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/142cc540828c66cbeff949e246e32086.webm?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/973450/extras/142cc540828c66cbeff949e246e32086.mp4?t=1619088916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
